com.faunadb.client.types

Class LazyValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.faunadb.client.types.LazyValue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Value

    public final class LazyValue
extends Object
implements Value
    A Value that wraps a JSON response tree. This Value does not convert to a concrete type until one of its type coercion methods is called.
